to the sewer network?

41
00:02:03,111 --> 00:02:05,492
Or shall we keep
on-site sanitation systems

42
00:02:05,591 --> 00:02:07,853
and plan for proper
faecal sludge management?

43
00:02:08,365 --> 00:02:13,890
Or maybe you would prefer alternatives,
such as decentralized sewer systems.

44
00:02:15,368 --> 00:02:18,623
So, what's an integrated
planning approach?

45
00:02:19,621 --> 00:02:23,631
First of all, it means planning for
the whole sanitation supply chain.

46
00:02:23,871 --> 00:02:28,809
as demonstrated behind me
from the latrine to (INAUDIBLE) disposal.

47
00:02:29,480 --> 00:02:31,329
