means also to have a holistic view

55
00:02:56,101 --> 00:02:58,381
where technology
is just one component,

56
00:02:58,601 --> 00:03:00,246
as shown in this figure.

57
00:03:00,331 --> 00:03:02,093
A view that takes into account

58
00:03:02,131 --> 00:03:04,148
the different socioeconomic context,

59
00:03:04,800 --> 00:03:08,617
people's aspirations
or the available financial resources,

60
00:03:08,687 --> 00:03:10,974
skills and management capacities.

61
00:03:11,432 --> 00:03:14,432
We need to understand
each area of a city

62
00:03:14,594 --> 00:03:16,256
with its specificities

63
00:03:16,617 --> 00:03:20,482
and then see how all can fit together
under one roof.

64
00:03:21,972 --> 00:03:24,804
All the elements I just mentioned
build what we call

65
00:03:24,844 --> 00:03:26,430
the enabling environment.

66
00:03:27,366 --> 00:03:30,753
The enabling environment
is a set of conditions

67
00:03:30,828 --> 00:03:32,670
that make your scheme work.

68
00:03:32,985 --> 00:03:36,429
As you can see, you need support
from the government,

69
00:03:36,473 --> 00:03:39,084
the proper legal
and regulatory framework.

70
00:03:39,284 --> 00:03:41,392
You need institutional arrangements,

71
00:03:41,584 --> 00:03:44,436
you need to check
the available skills and capacities,

72
00:03:44,636 --> 00:03:46,616
define financial arrangements,

73
00:03:46,816 --> 00:03:50,755
